    "updated_at": "2018-10-27T19:38:26Z",
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "This is indeed different to #10438.\r\n\r\nThe issue is with https://github.com/OpenRA/OpenRA/blob/e038b8674224ebb251773a5ab82bbc05042e5ace/OpenRA.Mods.Common/Traits/Render/WithWallSpriteBody.cs#L107-L110\r\n\r\nwhich unconditionally overwrites the make animation when the tower is damaged, transitioning to the `Light` damage state.\r\n\r\nThis isn't an issue in our shipping mods, which don't use a make animation with this trait, so moving back to the TS milestone."
